headline: Palantir Reported a Blowout Quarter, but Is the Stock Overvalued?

headline: Investors Are Piling Into Palantir Stock After Revenue Soars. Should You Follow?
summary: Palantir (NYSE: PLTR) has been one of the hottest stocks of the year, rising around 275% as of the time of writing.  Clearly, many investors are piling into Palantir's stock, but is that a good idea?  Palantir is an artificial intelligence (AI) company that made a name for itself by creating custom AI models for the government.
